description.en:
Fomolabs aims to be the most exclusive NFT management agency and marketplace on the Binance Smart Chain. All our NFT releases are vetted and by well-known musicians, athletes, celebrities, rappers, artists, digital creatives, and influencers.

Each month fomolabs partners with a world-renowned personality to put together an amazing set of digital and physical art products that can be redeemable for FOMO tokens or sold in the FOMO swap NFT exchange.

All tokens provided as collateral for entries will be added to the jackpot draw. The winner has the choice to burn the tokens forever, keep the tokens and leave the NFT for the next draw, exchange the nft with fomolabs for the private gallery at a pre-determined rate or keep the nft and try their luck on the FOMOSwap nft exchange!

Fomolabs is a creation built by a team of expert blockchain developers, digital artists, and creatives, influencers, celebrities & marketing professionals.
